Privacy Policy:

Tap Tap Chicken respects your privacy and is committed to protecting any personal information that you may provide while playing our game. Please note that Tap Tap Chicken does not collect, store, or share any of your personal data.

Information We Collect:
Tap Tap Chicken does not collect any personal information from players. We do not require players to create user accounts, and we do not gather any data about your identity, location, or device.

In-App Purchases:
Tap Tap Chicken may offer optional in-app purchases for additional game features or content. These purchases are processed directly through the app store provider (e.g., Apple App Store, Google Play Store), and Tap Tap Chicken does not have access to your payment information.

Advertising:
Tap Tap Chicken may display third-party advertisements within the game. These ads are served by ad networks, which may collect anonymous data about your device for the purpose of delivering targeted advertisements. However, Tap Tap Chicken does not have access to or control over the information collected by these ad networks.

Third-Party Links:
Tap Tap Chicken may contain links to external websites or services, such as social media platforms. Please note that we are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third-party sites. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of any website or service that you visit through Tap Tap Chicken.

Children's Privacy:
Tap Tap Chicken is intended for general audiences and does not knowingly collect any personal information from children under the age of 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us immediately so that we can take appropriate action.

Changes to This Privacy Policy:
Tap Tap Chicken may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify players of any significant changes by posting the updated policy within the game. By continuing to use Tap Tap Chicken after such changes are made, you agree to the revised Privacy Policy.

Contact Us:
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or Tap Tap Chicken's privacy practices, please contact us at santosh161616@gmail.com.
